    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "System Timetable\nEffective June 10, 1999\nWE JUST GOT\nANOTHER AWARD FOR\nDOING WHAT WE DO\nEVERY DAY.\nIMAGINE THAT.\nContinental was ranked highest in customer\nsatisfaction for long flights in 1996, 1997 and 1999 by\nFrequent Flyer magazine/J.D. Power and Associates*\nI.D. POWER\nPRESENTED IN PARTNERSHIP WITH\nfrequent flyer\nContinental Airlines\nWork Hard.\nFly Right..",
      "For reservations call your\ntravel agent or\n1-800-523-FARE\n(1-800-523-3273)\nFor complete vacation packages\ncall Continental Airlines Vacations at\n1-800-634-5555\nFor automated flight\ninformation call\n1-800-784-4444\nAlways ask for an\n#TICKET.\nPurchase tickets online at\nwww.continental.com\nContinental\nAirlines\n*Frequent Flyer magazine/J.D. Power and Associates 1996, 1997 and 1999\nairline customer satisfaction studies - U.S. flights™ 1999 study conducted\namong frequent airline travelers who completed 6,520 individual flight\nevaluations. Long flight is defined as 500 air miles or more."
    ],
